0.3
===

* Similar bug for null PylonSet handling entity explosions in nether/end.
* Made pylon xp rate recalculation an async task.
* Periodic save of pylon data.
* Bonus exp when crops & trees grow within the field.

0.2
===

* Reduction of fishing success in drained field.
* Reduction of spawning of passive mobs by natural, eggs and breeding.
* Fix bug with null PylonSet in nether/end for block break.
* Code tidying.
* Change pylon field strength to decrease linearly from centre to radius.

0.1
===

* Initial release
* Finding high energy spots by examining plants.
* Tower structure, basic function, damage detection.
* Crop growth negative effects.
